TWComponent.script: tw.local.sqlStatement select distinct ProcessApplication1 as ProcessApplication, snapshots, branches, toolkits, totalinstances, activeinstances, totaltasks, activetasks, totalusers, activeusers, totalartifacts, totalbpds from (select * from (select distinct lp.name as ProcessApplication1, count(distinct ls.snapshot_id) as snapshots, count(distinct ls.branch_id) as branches, count(distinct lpd.project_dependency_id) as toolkits from lsw_project lp, lsw_snapshot ls, lsw_po_versions lpv, LSW_PROJECT_DEPENDENCY lpd, LSW_SNAPSHOT ls1 , LSW_PROJECT lp1 where lp.project_id = ls.project_id and LPD.VERSION_ID = LPV.PO_VERSION_ID and LPV.BRANCH_ID = LS1.BRANCH_ID and LS1.PROJECT_ID = LP1.PROJECT_ID and lp1.project_id = lp.project_id and lp.is_toolkit = 'F' and ls.name is not null group by lp.name) q1 INNER JOIN (select distinct lp1.name as ProcessApplication2, count(distinct LBI1.BPD_INSTANCE_ID) as TotalInstances, COUNT(distinct (CASE WHEN LBI1.EXECUTION_STATUS = 1 THEN LBI1.BPD_INSTANCE_ID ELSE null END)) as ActiveInstances from LSW_PROJECT lp1, LSW_BPD_INSTANCE LBI1, LSW_BPD_STATUS_CODES where LBI1.EXECUTION_STATUS(+) = LSW_BPD_STATUS_CODES.STATUS_ID and lp1.PROJECT_ID = LBI1.PROJECT_ID(+) and lp1.is_toolkit = 'F' group by lp1.name) q2 ON q1.ProcessApplication1 = q2.ProcessApplication2 INNER JOIN (select distinct lp.name as ProcessApplication3, count(distinct lt.task_id) as TotalTasks, COUNT(distinct (CASE WHEN lt.status=12 and lt.activity_task_type = 1 and lt.execution_status = 3 THEN lt.task_id ELSE null END)) as ActiveTasks from lsw_project lp, lsw_snapshot ls, LSW_TASK lt where lp.project_id = ls.project_id and ls.snapshot_id = lt.snapshot_id(+) and lp.is_toolkit = 'F' and ls.name is not null group by lp.name) q3 ON q3.ProcessApplication3 = q2.ProcessApplication2 INNER JOIN (select distinct lp.name as ProcessApplication4, count(distinct lux.user_id) as TotalUsers, count(distinct (case when burp.ONLINE_STATUS = 'T' THEN lux.user_id else null END)) as ActiveUsers from lsw_project lp, lsw_snapshot ls, LSW_TASK lt, LSW_USR_XREF lux, BPM_USR_RUNTIME_PROPS burp where lp.project_id = ls.project_id and ls.snapshot_id = lt.snapshot_id(+) and lux.user_id(+) = lt.assumer_id and burp.user_id(+) = lux.user_id and lp.is_toolkit = 'F' and ls.name is not null group by lp.name) q4 ON q4.ProcessApplication4 = q3.ProcessApplication3 INNER JOIN (select distinct lp.name as ProcessApplication5, count(distinct lpr.target_id) as TotalArtifacts, count(distinct (case when lpr.target_type = 1 THEN lpr.target_id else null END)) as TotalBPDS from lsw_project lp, lsw_snapshot ls, lsw_po_versions lpv, LSW_PROJECT_DEPENDENCY lpd, LSW_SNAPSHOT ls1 , LSW_PROJECT lp1, LSW_BPD_STATUS_CODES, LSW_DEP_PATH ldp, lsw_po_reference lpr where lp.project_id = ls.project_id and LPD.VERSION_ID = LPV.PO_VERSION_ID and LPV.BRANCH_ID = LS1.BRANCH_ID and LS1.PROJECT_ID = LP1.PROJECT_ID and lp1.project_id = lp.project_id and LPD.PROJECT_DEPENDENCY_ID = LDP.DEPENDENCY_ID and LDP.DEP_PATH_ID = LPR.DEP_PATH_ID and lp.is_toolkit = 'F' and ls.name is not null group by lp.name) q5 ON q4.ProcessApplication4 = q5.ProcessApplication5)
